<p>You can download a <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/allegro-pas/files/5.2.b.1/furiouspaladin-5.2.b.1-bin-win32.zip/download">Game Demo</a> (Windows and WineHQ), a simple game that shows some of the capabilities of Allegro.pas.&nbsp; Such a simple game isn't enough to show everything that Allegro can offer.&nbsp; If you want to know more about what you can do with Allegro.pas, take a peek to the <a href="http://allegro-pas.sourceforge.net/docs/5.2/">documentation</a>.</p>
